overview: Everywhere in Artois, Juliette is said to treat sick cows. Juliette is a healer, for want of better, but her dream is to raise and sell animals. One evening, an unexpected opportunity arises: if she cares for a cow from the big Jourdel family, they could well hire her. But that night, the healing doesn’t go as planned.
title: Elle est des nôtres
